Package: rivR
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 21.12.2015
Title: River Research and Modelling
Author: Claude Flener <claude.flener@utu.fi>
Maintainer: Claude Flener <claude.flener@utu.fi>
Description: rivR is a collection of river research related R functions,
    including modelling and calibration algorithms as well as spatial data
    processing functions for modelling bathymetry and multidimensional flow fields.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0),
    rgdal,
    R.matlab,
    geometry,
    sp,
    RColorBrewer,
    classInt,
    maptools,
    raster
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
